{"id":19460,"type":4,"name":"Mini Ninjas","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/64/6c/19460_z8t98.jpg","rating":{"total":64,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":0,"4":2,"5":1,"6":13,"7":21,"8":21,"9":5,"10":0},"score":7.1},"summary":"Eidos在2009年8月26日正式公布了由旗下Elo Interactive工作室开发的卡通冒险游戏《迷你忍者》（Mini Ninjas），游戏包括PC、Wii、DS、Xbox360和PS3版本，手机平台上也有同名游戏。 　　\r\n在《迷你忍者》的世界中，玩家将扮演一个忍者小英雄来对抗邪恶武士，最终凭借自己出色的战斗技巧和忍术到达命运城堡，击败邪恶的督军来解救这个世界。 　　\r\nElo Interactive以前的作品都是以成年人为主，像是《杀手4：血钱》《凯恩与林奇之死人》等，本次转型之作开始强调超级可爱的卡通风格，不能不说是争取更大年龄范围玩家的一个好办法，Elo Interactive也希望这款转型之作能让上到80岁老人，下到10岁顽童都喜欢。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>迷你忍者</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/20363\">IO Interactive</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/17043\">Eidos Interactive</a></li><li><span>平台: </span>PC</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>动作冒险</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>1</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2009年9月9日</li>","collection":{"wish":5,"collect":78,"doing":1,"on_hold":6,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"ACT","count":18},{"name":"PC","count":16},{"name":"可爱的人设","count":10},{"name":"迷你忍者","count":6},{"name":"NDS","count":5},{"name":"2009","count":4},{"name":"XBOX360","count":3},{"name":"忍者","count":3},{"name":"STEAM","count":2},{"name":"RPG","count":1},{"name":"AAVG","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":20363,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/3a/d8/20363_prsn_uhIfr.jpg","name":"IO Interactive","desc":"开发"},{"id":17043,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/3c/71/17043_prsn_U3DbI.jpg","name":"艺夺","desc":"发行"}],"like":[{"id":1693,"name":"虐杀原形","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b5/9a/1693_Pa55y.jpg"},{"id":171,"name":"侠盗猎车手4","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/a4/a0/171_aus.jpg"},{"id":45,"name":"仙剑奇侠传四","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/6c/83/45_Hurm9.jpg"},{"id":6818,"name":"魔兽争霸3：冰封王座","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/a3/84/6818_MFmpB.jpg"},{"id":1859,"name":"植物大战僵尸","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/53/7d/1859_RuRuF.jpg"},{"id":796,"name":"DJMAX 携带版 2","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/35/cf/796_rQV5k.jpg"},{"id":899,"name":"名侦探柯南","image":"//